{"title":"莫高窟之花——看《丝路花雨》","authors":["杨柄"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":12,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫高窟之花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——看《丝路花雨》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年万手凿悬崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠无花窟有花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神笔走毫晕七彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天带我进云霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多姿多采菩萨像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数无名艺术家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丝去舞来绸作路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西文化汇中华。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}